{"tid":60413,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[AngularJS] Debug 求救......","createTime":"2016-12-30T12:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T18:13:23.000Z","uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a53d4439e393fffaecc02a5f78ce5bc0c53836","tid":60413,"uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 小弟寫緊個簡簡單單既login system<br />\n我寫左個custom service 係咁樣樣<br />\n<br />\n(function(){<br />\n\t'use strict';<br />\n<br />\n\tangular<br />\n\t\t.module('fypApp')<br />\n\t\t.factory('authentication', authentication);<br />\n<br />\n\tfunction authentication($http, $windows){<br />\n\t\t.....................}<br />\n<br />\n想 inject 落個 Controller 度<br />\n<br />\n(function(){<br />\n\t'use strict';<br />\n<br />\n\tangular<br />\n\t\t.module(&quot;fypApp&quot;)<br />\n\t\t.controller(&quot;signinCtrl&quot;, signinCtrl);<br />\n<br />\n\tfunction signinCtrl($scope, authentication){ ....}<br />\n<br />\n而我Check過index.html 裡面script 既順序係冇錯到<br />\n&lt;!-- Self-defined AngularJS modules --&gt;<br />\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;/js/app.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;/js/services/auth_service.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;/js/controllers/signin_controller.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一 inject authentication 依個service 落個controller度, 就會出左BUG<br />\n寫住<br />\nError: [$injector:unpr] <a href=\"http://errors.angularjs.org/1.6.1/$injector/unpr?p0=%24windowsProvider%20%3C-%20%24windows%20%3C-%20authentication\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ferrors.angularjs.org%2F1.6.1%2F%24injector%2Funpr%3Fp0%3D%2524windowsProvider%2520%253C-%2520%2524windows%2520%253C-%2520authentication&d=pqD1l52sv3WLqFU%2Bpjfs2WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0b140ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://errors.angularjs.org/1.6.1/$injector/unpr?p0=%24windowsProvider%20%3C-%20%24windows%20%3C-%20authentication</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇高手知道係發生緊咩緊... debug到我好頹廢<br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fcdca7d29995fbc0a24f78c025dc6a98a32490","tid":60413,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"$window ??"},{"pid":"9002886f821d80feee73d1ec6268d6740dd680b1","tid":60413,"uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$window ??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDude, you saved my day.<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來一直係我眼殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fefd0b04e69a340dd97115ddd14b87333bea0","tid":60413,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>$window ??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/